Output ../assets/demo/sandbox-enter.gif

Require orrery-bin

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 32
Set Width 1200
Set Height 1200

Hide
Type "source ~/.orrery/activate.sh"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "orrery enter work"
Sleep 0.5s
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "claude"
Sleep 0.5s
Enter
Sleep 10s

Type "/exit"
Sleep 0.5s
Enter
Sleep 3s

